25
00:00:50.093 --> 00:00:51.703
A Farway Tree.

26
00:00:51.703 --> 00:00:52.791
Watch.

27
00:00:54.097 --> 00:00:56.447
How does it do that?

28
00:00:56.447 --> 00:00:57.753
