60
00:02:58.482 --> 00:03:01.093
Okay. what are you looking for?

61
00:03:01.093 --> 00:03:03.661
I am not looking.
I am digging.

62
00:03:03.661 --> 00:03:06.795
Aha! Here it is.

63
00:03:06.795 --> 00:03:08.188
It's my secret stash.

64
00:03:11.060 --> 00:03:15.325
