76
00:03:53.015 --> 00:03:54.930
Baby. the party hasn't
even started yet.

77
00:03:54.930 --> 00:03:58.499
I know! I know!
That's why they call it pregame.

78
00:03:59.935 --> 00:04:00.718
What?

79
00:04:02.764 --> 00:04:04.113
Nothing.

80
00:04:04.113 --> 00:04:06.855
