81
00:04:06.855 --> 00:04:07.943
Yeah. I know.
I know. I know.

82
00:04:09.814 --> 00:04:11.033
Uh. Julie?

83
00:04:11.033 --> 00:04:12.948
How 'bout you?

84
00:04:12.948 --> 00:04:15.951
