176
00:12:12.557 --> 00:12:14.124
Well. but it's something.

177
00:12:15.647 --> 00:12:17.127
Yeah.

178
00:12:19.782 --> 00:12:22.132
Hey. Hey.

179
00:12:24.744 --> 00:12:27.834
It matters.

180
00:12:27.834 --> 00:12:29.792
