Hey. hey. hey.
Hey! Hold on.

188
00:12:54.730 --> 00:12:56.514
-Hey.
-Maybe slow down a little bit.

189
00:12:56.514 --> 00:12:57.820
Hey. I'm I'm fine.
I'm fine.

190
00:12:57.820 --> 00:12:59.648
It's a party. right?

191
00:12:59.648 --> 00:13:01.432
Don't worry.

192
00:13:04.653 --> 00:13:06.742
