-We should go.

197
00:13:16.447 --> 00:13:17.753
Yeah. yeah. yes.

198
00:13:17.753 --> 00:13:21.496
Hey. shut your fucking mouths!

199
00:13:23.498 --> 00:13:25.543
All right.

200
00:13:25.543 --> 00:13:27.937
We are here tonight

201
00:13:27.937 --> 00:13:31.332
