261
00:17:35.837 --> 00:17:37.621
strict...

262
00:17:39.797 --> 00:17:43.149
...rigid.

263
00:17:43.149 --> 00:17:47.109
And I get it. Parents.
they worry about their kids.

264
00:17:47.109 --> 00:17:49.720
